1 people of this State, and it is therefore imperative that North Carolina reach the average of teacher
2 salary in the southeastern United States by 2032. Therefore, there is appropriated from the
3 General Fund to the Reserve the following amounts for each fiscal year to be used for the
4 purposes set forth in this section:
